nervous system
Organ System, Neurologic
Neurologic Body System
Nervous System
Body System, Neurologic
Neurologic""" ;
                                                            :definition "The entire nerve apparatus, composed of a central part, the brain and spinal cord, and a peripheral part, the cranial and spinal nerves, autonomic ganglia, and plexuses." ;
                                                            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12755" ;
                                                            rdfs:label "Nervous System" .


###  http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12756
