peritoneal cavity
BODY CAVITY, PERITONEAL""" ;
                                                            :definition "The potential space located between the parietal and visceral layers of the peritoneum." ;
                                                            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12769" ;
                                                            rdfs:label "Peritoneal Cavity" .


###  http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12787
<http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12787> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                            rdfs:subClassOf <http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C13018> ;
