TONSIL
Tonsil
Tonsils
tonsil""" ;
                                                            :definition "The two organs situated in the throat on either side of the narrow passage from the mouth to the pharynx. They are composed of lymphoid tissues." ;
                                                            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C12802" ;
                                                            rdfs:label "Tonsil" .


