                                                                           :reference "Acute Physiology and Chronic Health Evaluation II (APACHE II) (Knaus WA, Draper EA, Wagner DP, Zimmerman JE. APACHE II: a severity of disease classification system. Critical Care Medicine 1985; 13(10):818-29). CDISC believes this instrument to be in the public domain, but you should perform your own assessment." ,
