            :Synonyms """Carbamic acid, (3-(((4-aminophenyl)sulfonyl)(2-methylpropyl)amino)-2-hydroxy-1-(- phenylmethyl)propyl)-, tetrahydro-3-furanyl ester, (3S-(3R*(1S*,2R*)))-141W94
AMPRENAVIR
Agenerase
Amprenavir
KVX 478
VX 478""" ;
