                      :Synonyms """Anthelminthic Agent
Antihelminthic Agent
Anthelmintic Agent
Antihelminthic Drugs
Antihelminthics
Anthelminthics
Vermifuges""" ;
                      :definition "A pharmacological agent that can kill or prevent the reproduction of parasitic helminths, including nematodes, flukes and tapeworms." ;
                      :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C250" ;
                      rdfs:label "Antihelminthic Agent" .


