                                       :Synonyms """elastase-alpha-1-antiprotease complex
2-AAT
elastase alpha-1-proteinase inhibitor complex
alpha-ATE complex
alpha-AT elastase complex
elastase alpha1-antitrypsin
Neutrophilic elastase-alpha 1-antitrypsin
alpha 1-antitrypsin-leukocyte elastase complex""" ;
                                       :reference "http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/MESH/C037741" ;
                                       rdfs:label "Elastase-alpha-1-antiprotease Complex" .


