                                            :Synonyms """Erythrocyte sedimentation rate (ESR)
sedimentation rate
Erythrocyte Sedimentation Rate Measurement
Erythrocyte Sedimentation Rate
erythrocyte sedimentation rate
Biernacki Reaction
ESR
Sed Rate""" ;
                                            :definition "A quantitative measurement of the distance that red blood cells travel in one hour in a sample of unclotted blood." ;
                                            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C74611" ;
                                            rdfs:label "Erythrocyte Sedimentation Rate Measurement" .


