Esophagus - mucosa
esophagus mucosa
esophageal mucous membrane
mucosa of esophagus
mucous membrane of esophagus""" ;
                   :definition "The lining of the esophagus. It is composed of non-keratinized stratified squamous epithelium, lamina propria, and muscularis mucosa." ;
                   :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C32538" ;
