Hyaluronan Synthase 2
Synthase, Hyaluronan
Synthetase, Hyaluronate
Hyaluronate Synthase
hasA Enzyme
Synthases, Hyaluronan
Hyaluronan Synthase 1""" ;
                      :definition "Membrane-associated glucuronosyltransferases that catalyze the reaction of UDP-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine and UDP-D-glucuronate to produce HYALURONAN. HYALURONAN SYNTHASE 2 (HAS2) is essential for embryogenesis and its expression by tumor cells is associated with metastasis." ;
