Immune-Mediated Coagulopathy
IMC""" ;
                              :definition "Disorders of coagulation caused by autoantibodies generated against native coagulation factors or therapeutically-administered hemostatic agents." ;
                              :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C131673" ;
                              rdfs:label "Immune-Mediated Coagulopathy" .


