Mannose Binding Protein
Lectin, Mannan-Binding
Mannose-Binding Protein
Mannan Binding Lectin
Mannan Binding Protein
Mannose Binding Lectin
Mannan-Binding Protein
Mannan-Binding Lectin
MBL""" ;
                        :definition "A specific mannose-binding member of the collectin family of lectins. It binds to carbohydrate groups on invading pathogens and plays a key role in the MANNOSE-BINDING LECTIN COMPLEMENT PATHWAY." ;
                        :reference "http://purl.bioontology.org/ontology/MESH/D037601" ;
                        rdfs:label "Mannose-Binding Lectin" .


