Neutrophils/Lymphocytes
NEUTLY
NLR""" ;
                                            :definition "The determination of the ratio of neutrophils compared to lymphocytes present in a biological sample. The measurement may be expressed as a ratio or percentage." ;
                                            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C141271" ;
                                            rdfs:label "Neutrophil to Lymphocyte Ratio Measurement" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/zchero/ontologies/2023/11/SepsisOntology#Nevirapine
:Nevirapine rdf:type owl:Class ;
            rdfs:subClassOf :Non-nucleoside_Reverse_Transcriptase_Inhibitor ;
            :Synonyms """11-Cyclopropyl-5,11-dihydro-4-methyl-6H-dipyrido(3,2-b:2',3'-e)(1,4)diazepin-6-one
BI-RG-587
BIRG 0587
NEVIRAPINE
NVP
Nevirapine
Viramune""" ;
            :definition "A benzodiazepine non-nucleoside reverse transcriptase inhibitor. In combination with other antiretroviral drugs, nevirapine reduces HIV viral loads and increases CD4 counts, thereby retarding or preventing the damage to the immune system and reducing the risk of developing AIDS." ;
            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C29277" ;
            rdfs:label "Nevirapine" .


