Thrombophilia Related to COVID-19""" ;
                                   :definition "Thrombophilia in a patient with probable or confirmed acute COVID-19." ;
                                   :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C191638" ;
                                   rdfs:label "Thrombophilia Related to COVID-19" .


