                                                                              :reference "Li Y, Wang C, Chen M. Metabolomics-based study of potential biomarkers of sepsis. Sci Rep. 2023 Jan 11;13(1):585. doi: 10.1038/s41598-022-24878-z. PMID: 36631483; PMCID: PMC9834301." ;
