Placental Anticoagulant Protein I
Placental Anticoagulant Protein 4
Placental Protein 4
Thromboplastin Inhibitor
Vascular Anticoagulant-Alpha
Calphobindin I
ANNEXIN A5
ANXA5
Annexin A5
Annexin V
Annexin-5
CBP-I
PAP-I
PP4
VAC-Alpha""" ;
