ApoB-100""" ;
                      :definition "Apolipoprotein B-100 (4563 aa, ~516 kDa) is encoded by the human APOB gene. This protein plays a role in both transport and cellular uptake of LDL particles." ;
                      :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C106032" ;
                      rdfs:label "Apolipoprotein B-100" .


:Apolipoprotein_M :Synonyms """NG20-Like Protein
Apolipoprotein M
Protein G3a
APOM
Apo-M
ApoM""" ;
                  :definition "Apolipoprotein M (188 aa, ~21 kDa) is encoded by the human APOM gene. This protein is involved in fatty acid transport." ;
                  :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C178705" ;
                  rdfs:label "Apolipoprotein M" .


:Argatroban :Synonyms """1-[5-guanidino-2-[(3-methyl-1,2,3,4-tetrahydroquinolin-8-yl)sulfonylamino]pentanoyl]-4-methyl-piperidine-2-carboxylic acid
ARGATROBAN
Argatroban
Argipidine
MD-805""" ;
            :definition "A synthetic derivative of L-arginine with antithrombotic activity. Argatroban is a univalent and direct inhibitor of fibrin-bound thrombin. This agent reversibly binds to the thrombin active site thereby preventing the thrombin-dependent reactions, which include conversion of fibrinogen to fibrin; the activation of factors V, VIII and XI; the activation of protein C; and platelet aggregation. Argatroban is highly selective for thrombin and is able to inhibit the action of both free and clot-associated thrombin. As a result, stabilization of blood clots and coagulation is inhibited." ;
            :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C28833" ;
            rdfs:label "Argatroban" .


:Arginine-Vasopressin :Synonyms """Arginine-Vasopressin
Arginine Vasopressin
Arg-Vasopressin
Vasopressin
Antidiuretic Hormone
ADH
AVP""" ;
                      :definition "Arginine-vasopressin (9 aa, ~1 kDa) is encoded by the human AVP gene. This protein is involved in peripheral blood vessel vasoconstriction and antidiuretic action in the kidney." ;
                      :reference "http://ncicb.nci.nih.gov/xml/owl/EVS/Thesaurus.owl#C2285" ;
                      rdfs:label "Arginine-Vasopressin" .


