DEXAMETHASONE
1-Dehydro-16alpha-methyl-9alpha-fluorohydrocortisone
Dexafluorene
Aacidexam
Adexone
Alba-Dex
Alin
Alin Depot
Auxiloson
Baycadron
Baycuten
Baycuten N
Decacort
Decadrol
Decadron
Decalix
